trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollectionEnumerator"></xref> class.
The <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection"></xref> for which to create the enumerator.
Gets the current element in the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection"></xref>.
Advances the enumerator to the next element of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollection"></xref>.
`true` if the enumerator was successfully advanced to the next element; `false` if the enumerator was past the end of the collection.
Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection.
For a description of this member, see the <xref href="System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current"></xref> property.
This member is an explicit interface member implementation.
It can be used only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Design.Behavior.BehaviorServiceAdornerCollectionEnumerator> instance is cast to an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator> interface.
